tosdr.case: The service informs users that its privacy policy does not apply to third party websites

title: The service informs users that its privacy policy does not apply to third party websites
quoteText: The applications used by the Users on the Site are placed and supported by third parties (developers) which act independently and not on behalf of the Site Administration. The Users should familiarize themselves with the service rules and personal data protection policy of such third persons (developers) before beginning to use the applications.
